      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Hard Stop Errors",
      "position": {
        "x": -120,
        "y": 420
      },
      "width": 720,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Error Conditions (Hard Stop)\n\n- schema violation\n- invalid port reference\n- missing dependency\n- forbidden mutation\n- identity loss\n- intent/content mismatch\n\nAny error aborts execution and persistence.",
        "_classBinding": {
